result.adr_address: 1 Kornhill Rd, Kornhill, Hong Kong
result.name: TeaWood Taiwanese Cafe & Restaurant

reviews.text: Cosy Taiwanese cafe in Kornhill Plaza. Afternoon tea set menu is available at 2:30-5:30pm. Fried shrimp rolls with fried chicken pieces tasted average. Bubble tea had a lot of milk in it, more than I preferred.
We came for dessert. It was alright! I ordered the lavender milk tea with pearls and I give it a 7/10, my mom had the bowl and give it a 7/10 as well - beautiful decor though!

A Taiwanese chain food store and no surprise with food quality and standard while it wasn't bad. Set lunch was more cost effective with a free drink offered. Today we had duck, braised pork knuckle and curry beef briskets which wasn't spicy at all. Add a certain amount of money u hv more choices on drinks that I had hot fruit tea, my recommended drink option.

Very rude service staff. Went there for lunch today in a party of 6. Two of the set lunches (same dish) took a long time (35 min from ordering) as the rest of the party was already finishing up their food. We followed up with the staff twice. When the waitress brought 1 of the missing set, I told her that we have one more, to which she responded "it's coming, can you not chase after it anymore?" in a rude voice (her name is Nicole). We thought we heard her incorrectly, but we did not. We asked the cashier if they have any comment card when paying and he asked his manager to come. The manager told us they don't have any so I told him one of his staff is very rude, but he didn't seem to care and didn't ask who or any follow-up questions. They clearly do not deserve the 10% "service" charge.

1) bring dessert BEFORE main course?! Nonsence!👎
2) very slow service👎
3) very good food👍

result.adr_address: 香港康山康山道1號
result.name: 茶木 · 台式休閒餐廳

reviews.text: 蚵仔四色麵的麵有口感，不會太淋，湯底濃度適中，味道不錯，但蚵仔份量不多，只有三幾隻食到鮮味，方魚也比較硬，可以做得更好。台式食店，菜牌以味濃香口食物為主，有小菜，有麵食，也有西式多士甜品等，更有多款以生果做的凍飲。環境座椅舒適，服務還可以，但平日食飯時間好多時也要排隊等位。
食物質素高，看得出每一道菜式都係精心設計，色香味俱全。而且價錢合理，難怪經過大排長龍。

Cosy Taiwanese cafe in Kornhill Plaza. Afternoon tea set menu is available at 2:30-5:30pm. Fried shrimp rolls with fried chicken pieces tasted average. Bubble tea had a lot of milk in it, more than I preferred.
點了牛腩麵跟蚵仔煎 ，一款就煮得未夠時間 麵條未煮散 好硬，另一款就煮得過長咗 蚵仔煎好似乾咗啲，味道算係唔錯的。
We came for dessert. It was alright! I ordered the lavender milk tea with pearls and I give it a 7/10, my mom had the bowl and give it a 7/10 as well - beautiful decor though!
